::Hot Rod::

He looked at Feline. 
"You sels destructed, in the battle with the Mafia."
He looked at the others for explenations. She had blown up, beyond
repair. Despite this he left her parts in the CR. And now, here she was
alive, and she didn't seem to remember her death. Not that he was mad.
He was over joyed that his love was back.
